data.description: The sellers are offering $4,000 towards INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN for the buyer of this home built in 2019. This 3 bedroom 2 bath on a FULL BASEMENT with a fenced back yard is the one you've been waiting for. Featuring an OPEN CONCEPT FLOOR PLAN, cathedral ceiling and a primary bedroom, private bath and walk in closet you won't need to look any farther. Also the lower level is plumbed for a full bath that has already been started. All located on a quiet street.  Call today to schedule a private tour.
